{
  "texts": [
    "This extended Tanner graph also has an implementation in a thickness-2 architecture through the A and B edges (Methods).",
    "Articlerespectively.",
    "In total, the encoding relies on 2n physical qubits.",
    "The net encoding rate is therefore r = k/(2n).",
    "For example, the standard surface code architecture encodes k = 1 logical qubit into n = d 2 data qubits for a distance-d code and uses n - 1 check qubits for syndrome measurements."
  ]
}